data.description: This home has views, views, views!! The spacious main level overlooks the golf course with12 foot ceiling heights. As you enter into the home, the entry flows into the living and dining area with a third space that offers a fireplace. Off the living area is a enclosed sunroom. The Kitchen has an informal dining area and island seating, with a planning area and pantry. The large covered back patio and deck area are great for entertaining. The main level master bedroom features a 5 piece bath, walk-in closet and with an additional room attached that can be utilized as an office or nursery. There is a Main level laundry area and a 1/2 bath for guests. As you go down the stairs there is a walk out lower level with a large entertainment/game area, wet bar and 3 additional bedrooms, each with walk-in closets. Two additional bathrooms make it convenient for family living. Located in the utility room another Washer and Dryer hook up is available as well. There are two furnaces and central air units. But wait...the solar panels will help with energy efficiency. The walk out basement opens to the backyard with garden paths and a fenced backyard. The three car garage is oversized with a charging station for an electric car. The front circular drive gives additional parking. The HOA offers a club house with a swimming pool and tennis courts.
